[[File:Emberizacitronella3.png|thumb|Geographic distribution of the '''yellowhammer'''.]]
===Alternative forms===
* {{alt|en|yellow-ammer|yellow-hammer}}
===Etymology===
Alteration (influenced by {{m|en|hammer}}) of earlier {{m|en|yelambre}}, {{m|en|yelamber}}, from {{inh|en|enm|*yelwambre}}, from {{m|enm|yelwe||yellow}} + {{m|enm|*ambre||yellowhammer}}, from {{der|en|ang|amore}}, related to {{cog|goh|amaro||yellowhammer}} (see modern {{cog|de|Ammer}}).
===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# A [[passerine]] [[bird]], {{m|mul|Emberiza citrinella}}, of western [[Eurasia]], which is mainly yellow in colour.
#: {{syn|en|yellow bunting|ammer|yelamber|yeorling|yowley|yeldrin|yite}}
# {{lb|en|US}} The [[northern flicker]], ''[[Colaptes auratus]]''.
# A native or resident of the American state of [[Alabama]].
